    <item>
      <title>当卢特尼克（Lutnick）推动更大的投资时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-chip-grants-in-limbo-as-lutnick-pushes-for-bigger-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据八个熟悉此事的人说，商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）表示，他可以扣留筹码的筹款活动，因为他为联邦半导体补贴提供了一致的公司，以大大扩展其美国项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-chip-grants-in-limbo-as-lutnick-pushes-for-bigger-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 02:38:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列说，贝鲁特郊区罢工目标的真主党特工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/israel-says-hezbollah-operative-targeted-in-beirut-suburb-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方在贝鲁特郊区进行了一次空袭，该郊区以真主党的特工为目标，几天前自11月开始停火以来就袭击了黎巴嫩首都。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/israel-says-hezbollah-operative-targeted-in-beirut-suburb-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 02:16:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理说，美国的贸易目标“不努力谈判”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/australian-pm-says-us-trade-targets-are-not-up-for-negotiation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯（Anthony Albanese）拒绝了美国贸易机构对他国家的生物安全法和补贴医学系统的担忧，宣称他们“不愿意进行谈判”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/australian-pm-says-us-trade-targets-are-not-up-for-negotiation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 02:01:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国周五裁定尹恩总统的弹each</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/south-korea-to-rule-on-president-yoon-s-impeachment-on-april-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国有望就弹each总统Yoon Suk Yeol的政治命运裁决，决定是否将他永久撤离他的短暂武术法令或恢复他的命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/south-korea-to-rule-on-president-yoon-s-impeachment-on-april-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 01:48:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税在日本的危险危机恐惧，因为Ishiba誓言支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-tariffs-may-spell-economic-crisis-for-japan-onodera-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府的关税迫使日本政府争先恐后地为企业提出支持措施，因为担心征税可能会对亚洲国家造成重大的经济危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-tariffs-may-spell-economic-crisis-for-japan-onodera-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 01:48:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国领导人否决法案，以扩大董事会的职责向股东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/korea-leader-vetoes-bill-to-broaden-board-duties-to-shareholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国代理总统否决了一项具有里程碑意义的法案，该法案将加剧公司董事会对股东的责任，并与企业集团与改革倡导者争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/korea-leader-vetoes-bill-to-broaden-board-duties-to-shareholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 00:47:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在台湾附近开始更多的演习，向我们推回我们</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-holds-more-drills-near-taiwan-stepping-up-pressure-on-lai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国在台湾周围举行军事演习，涉及近一年的海军船只；在美国发誓要阻止北京在该地区的侵略之后的举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-holds-more-drills-near-taiwan-stepping-up-pressure-on-lai</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:53:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普弗里德曼（Floats Floats Floats Floats）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-floats-friedman-grenell-as-possible-picks-for-un-envoy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统浮动了前美国驻以色列戴维·弗里德曼（David Friedman）和特使里克·格雷内尔（Ric Grenell）作为联合国大使的潜在选秀权，此前一个狭窄的众议院共和党多数派撤销了代表埃利斯·斯特凡尼克（Elise Stefanik）的提名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-floats-friedman-grenell-as-possible-picks-for-un-envoy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:41:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的中国牙套报告将为交易谈判设定阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-review-of-china-trade-deal-to-add-to-xi-trump-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在习近平达平（Xi Jinping）达成了与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）达成的第一项贸易协议后，美国官员将在可能会在高风险的一周中对北京对这种讨价还价的遵守来表达他们的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-review-of-china-trade-deal-to-add-to-xi-trump-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党人起诉特朗普，以全面的“选举诚信”秩序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-sued-over-order-to-require-proof-of-citizenship-to-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的行政命令指导美国注册选民的方式进行重大变化，并将邮寄选票挑战为违宪的，这是民主党全国委员会和一组非营利组织提起的单独诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-sued-over-order-to-require-proof-of-citizenship-to-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 20:36:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
